Type: Package
Package: fingR
Title: A package to support sediment source fingerprinting studies 
Version: 1.1.0
Authors:
  person("Thomas", "Chalaux-Clergue",  role = c("aut","cre"), email = "thomaschalaux@icloud.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3525-832X")),
  person("Rémi", "Bizeul", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "rbizeul59@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4103-9839"))
Maintainer:
  The package maintainer <thomaschalaux@icloud.com> and <rbizeul59@gmail.com>
Description:
  A package to support sediment source fingerprinting studies:
  characterising your dataset, selecting tracers (three-step method), modelling source contribution (BMM) and assessing the quality of modelling
  predictions using virtual mixtures (support BMM and MixSIAR).
Depends:
  R (>= 4.2.2)
