  klaR (>= 1.7-2),
  MASS (>= 7.3-60)
Suggests:
  MixSIAR (>= 3.1.12),
  reshape2 (>= 1.4.4),
  tibble (>= 3.1.8),
  ape (>= 5.7-2)
